<TEXT>
   Imprisoned auto heir John Francis
Dodge must pay his ex-wife more than $50,000 in alimony and
attorney fees and $1,200 a month in child support, a judge has
ruled.
   Palm Beach Circuit Judge John D. Wessel on Thursday ordered
Dodge to begin making the monthly payments to Karen Christine Dodge
on June 1. They were married in September 1979, and he filed for
