of Staley Continental Inc., the nation's second largest refiner of
corn sweeteners, plan to announce their response to a $1.33 billion
buyout offer from Tate & Lyle PLC, a major British sugar refiner
and distributor.
   WASHINGTON _ The Treasury is to report on the government's
budget deficit for March; release time uncertain.
</TEXT>
<BYLINE>SATURDAY, April 23</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
   
   VIENNA, Austria _ OPEC's pricing committee is to meet with
officials from non-OPEC oil-producing nations, and perhaps Texas,
to discuss ways to bolster oil prices.
   WASHINGTON _ Effective today, federal law prohibits smoking on
all airline flights of two hours or less.
